For over 175 years, the manufacture has created a wealth of different models, many of which count among the timepieces most admired and sought after by connoisseurs and collectors. Self-winding mechanical movement. Caliber CH 28‑520 IRM QA 24H. Flyback chronograph. Annual Calendar. Matte blue opaline, 8 baguette diamond hour markers (~0.23 ct). Platinum case. Sapphire crystal case back. Water-resistant to 30 m. Case diameter: 40.5 mm. Height: 13.53 mm. Bezel set with 36 baguette diamonds (~3.48 ct). Fold-over clasp set with 22 baguette diamonds (~0.97 ct). Alligator strap with square scales, hand-stitched, shiny navy blue. Fold-over clasp.
